| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3741 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0b115d12-6e1e-5cab-bd8a-74de5fb7c1fe"
